headline.print_headline: Pryor's 'Obamacare' Ad Highlights His Cancer Fight
headline.main: Pryor's 'Obamacare' Ad Highlights His Cancer Fight

lead_paragraph: U.S. Sen. Mark Pryor reached into his own medical history Tuesday to explain his vote on the nation's new health care law, telling Arkansans his battle with a rare cancer 18 years ago influenced him.
